		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Progress keeps on continuing.  I got ICE to work.  It wasn't as horrible as I was thinking...  So I'm almost ready to start doing the process of adding enemies and general game design.
<br />
<br />Still have a few things to do like shooting and dying (no, you actually can't die yet!)
<br />
<br />This time around has been significantly easier.
<br />
<br />I may post a video or something when a general engine comes together.

		

		</td>
